posts.title: Is React really the right way to go?
posts.message: I'm not sure why React is the No.1 web framework/library right now. It just feels so unintuitive with the idea of functional component with dependencies, side-effects and hooks with the logic got spreaded all over the place. Such a pain in the butt to grasp the flow of the logic of my web page.

posts.title: Why do people keep shouting "PHP is Dead" always?
posts.message: So, there are a lot of toxic devs who keep saying PHP is sh*t and is dead. It has no future etc. But for me, I really love it. So why do some hate it so much? And does it actually have no future? And is Laravel so bad?

posts.title: How can I stay motivated?
posts.message: I have started coding in Python as my first coding language recently and I am starting to have trouble with motivation (I was told by a friend that this is common at first). But he didn’t really give a very specific was to avoid stopping because of this. I don’t want to stop coding because I kind of need coding to do my hopefully future job.
